---
layout: layouts/base.njk
pagination:
  data: languages
  size: 1
  alias: lang
permalink: "{% if lang == 'en' %}/en/guides/devsecops/{% else %}/guias/devsecops/{% endif %}"
seoTitle: "DevSecOps: Guia Completo 2026 com Pipeline e KPIs | Evernow"
seoDescription: "O que é DevSecOps, como implementar do shift-left ao shift-right, ferramentas SAST/DAST/SCA/IaC/DSPM no pipeline CI/CD, KPIs executivos e erros a evitar."
seoKeywords: "devsecops, o que é devsecops, como implementar devsecops, guia devsecops, shift left, devsecops ci cd, consultoria devsecops"
langPtUrl: "/guias/devsecops/"
langEnUrl: "/en/guides/devsecops/"
---
{% set urlPrefix = "" if lang == "pt" else "/en" %}
{% set langPtUrl = "/guias/devsecops/" %}
{% set langEnUrl = "/en/guides/devsecops/" %}
{% set breadcrumbs = [
  { label: ("Home" if lang == "en" else "Início"), url: urlPrefix + "/" },
  { label: ("Guides" if lang == "en" else "Guias"), url: (urlPrefix + "/guides/") if lang == "en" else "/guias/" },
  { label: "DevSecOps" }
] %}

<div class="header-and-banner-con w-100">
  <div class="header-and-banner-inner-con overlay-content">
    {% include "components/header.njk" %}
    {% include "components/breadcrumbs.njk" %}

    <section class="banner-main-con ev-hero" style="padding:60px 0 50px;">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row align-items-center">
          <div class="col-lg-7 wow slideInLeft">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:center;margin-bottom:18px;">
              <span style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.12);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.3);color:#00e0a3;font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.1em;padding:4px 12px;border-radius:20px;">{% if lang == "en" %}Pillar guide · Secure Code{% else %}Guia pilar · Secure Code{% endif %}</span>
              <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-size:.78rem;"><i class="fas fa-clock" style="margin-right:5px;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}12 min read{% else %}12 min de leitura{% endif %}</span>
              <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.4);font-size:.78rem;"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt" style="margin-right:5px;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Updated Apr 2026{% else %}Atualizado Abr 2026{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <h1 style="font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:800;line-height:1.15;">
              {% if lang == "en" %}DevSecOps: the <span style="color:#00e0a3;">complete guide</span> 2026{% else %}DevSecOps: o <span style="color:#00e0a3;">guia completo</span> de 2026{% endif %}
            </h1>
            <p class="ev-hero__sub mt-3">
              {% if lang == "en" %}What DevSecOps really is, how to go from shift-left to shift-right, which tools enter the CI/CD pipeline, executive KPIs and the four mistakes that kill 80% of programs.{% else %}O que DevSecOps é de verdade, como sair do shift-left para o shift-right, quais ferramentas entram no pipeline CI/CD, KPIs executivos e os quatro erros que matam 80% dos programas.{% endif %}
            </p>
            <div class="ev-hero__trust mt-4">
              <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}Pipeline + tooling{% else %}Pipeline + tooling{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}Executive KPIs{% else %}KPIs executivos{% endif %}</span>
              <span class="ev-hero__trust-item"><i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i> {% if lang == "en" %}Common mistakes{% else %}Erros comuns{% endif %}</span>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-4 d-flex flex-wrap" style="gap:14px;">
              <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/contact" class="contact-btn">{% if lang == "en" %}Talk to a DevSecOps specialist{% else %}Fale com especialista DevSecOps{% endif %}</a>
              <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/produtos/devsecops/" class="ev-btn-outline">{% if lang == "en" %}See managed service{% else %}Ver serviço gerenciado{% endif %}</a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-lg-5 wow slideInRight mt-5 mt-lg-0">
            <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.05);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.2);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;">
              <p style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.78rem;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;margin-bottom:16px;">{% if lang == "en" %}What you'll find here{% else %}O que você vai encontrar{% endif %}</p>
              <ul class="list-unstyled" style="font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);margin:0;">
                <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:10px;font-size:.75rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Definition beyond the buzzword{% else %}Definição além do buzzword{% endif %}</li>
                <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:10px;font-size:.75rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Shift-left vs shift-right model{% else %}Modelo shift-left vs shift-right{% endif %}</li>
                <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:10px;font-size:.75rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}8-stage reference pipeline{% else %}Pipeline de referência em 8 estágios{% endif %}</li>
                <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:10px;font-size:.75rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}7 KPIs the board understands{% else %}7 KPIs que o board entende{% endif %}</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:10px;font-size:.75rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}4 mistakes that kill programs{% else %}4 erros que matam programas{% endif %}</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<main>

  <!-- DEFINIÇÃO -->
  <section class="ev-section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Definition{% else %}Definição{% endif %}</div>
          <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}What DevSecOps actually is{% else %}O que é DevSecOps de verdade{% endif %}</h2>
          <div style="background:rgba(0,224,163,.06);border-left:4px solid #00e0a3;border-radius:0 12px 12px 0;padding:24px 28px;margin:24px 0 20px;" class="wow fadeInUp">
            <p style="font-size:1.08rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);line-height:1.75;margin:0;">{% if lang == "en" %}DevSecOps is the <strong>culture, practices and automation</strong> that integrate security into every stage of the application lifecycle — from ideation to production operation — with <em>shared</em> responsibility between development, security and operations.{% else %}DevSecOps é a <strong>cultura, práticas e automação</strong> que integram segurança em todas as etapas do ciclo de vida da aplicação — da ideação à operação em produção — com responsabilidade <em>compartilhada</em> entre desenvolvimento, segurança e operações.{% endif %}</p>
          </div>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);line-height:1.7;">{% if lang == "en" %}It is not "SAST inside GitHub Actions". That is a <strong>tactic</strong>. DevSecOps is the <strong>operating model</strong> that makes the tactic sustainable.{% else %}Não é "SAST dentro do GitHub Actions". Isso é <strong>tática</strong>. DevSecOps é o <strong>modelo operacional</strong> que torna a tática sustentável.{% endif %}</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- SHIFT-LEFT / SHIFT-RIGHT -->
  <section class="ev-section ev-section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Operating model{% else %}Modelo operacional{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Shift-left AND shift-right{% else %}Shift-left E shift-right{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 wow fadeInLeft">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;height:100%;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:4px;height:100%;background:#00e0a3;border-radius:14px 0 0 14px;"></div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;">
              <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:rgba(0,224,163,.12);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left" style="color:#00e0a3;"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#00e0a3;margin:0;">Shift-Left</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.7;">{% if lang == "en" %}Move security to the earliest possible moment: IDE, pre-commit, pull request. Cost of correction grows 10× per phase, so the earlier, the cheaper.{% else %}Puxar segurança para o momento mais cedo possível: IDE, pré-commit, pull request. Custo de correção cresce 10× por fase, quanto antes, mais barato.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding-left:0;list-style:none;">
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Threat Modeling on the story{% else %}Threat Modeling na story{% endif %}</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>SAST + secret scanning pre-commit</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>SCA on every new dependency</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>IaC Security (Checkov, tfsec)</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#00e0a3;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Security tests in unit/integration suite{% else %}Testes de segurança no suite unit/integration{% endif %}</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6 mb-4 wow fadeInRight">
          <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);border-radius:14px;padding:28px;height:100%;position:relative;overflow:hidden;">
            <div style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:4px;height:100%;background:#5b8fff;border-radius:14px 0 0 14px;"></div>
            <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:14px;">
              <div style="width:40px;height:40px;background:rgba(91,143,255,.12);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <i class="fas fa-arrow-right" style="color:#5b8fff;"></i>
              </div>
              <h4 style="color:#5b8fff;margin:0;">Shift-Right</h4>
            </div>
            <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);line-height:1.7;">{% if lang == "en" %}Security does not stop at deploy. Production behaves differently: real traffic, misconfiguration, drift, third-party risk. You need runtime observability.{% else %}Segurança não termina no deploy. Produção se comporta diferente: tráfego real, misconfig, drift, risco de terceiros. Precisa de observabilidade runtime.{% endif %}</p>
            <ul style="margin-top:14px;font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding-left:0;list-style:none;">
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#5b8fff;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>RASP (Runtime Application Self-Protection)</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#5b8fff;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>CSPM + CWPP + CNAPP</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#5b8fff;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>{% if lang == "en" %}Continuous external DAST{% else %}DAST externo contínuo{% endif %}</li>
              <li class="mb-2"><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#5b8fff;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>Attack Surface Management (ASM)</li>
              <li><i class="fas fa-check" style="color:#5b8fff;margin-right:8px;font-size:.8rem;"></i>Security chaos engineering</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PIPELINE 8 ESTÁGIOS -->
  <section class="ev-section bg-overly-img">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Reference pipeline{% else %}Pipeline de referência{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}DevSecOps pipeline in 8 stages{% else %}Pipeline DevSecOps em 8 estágios{% endif %}</h2>
      <p class="ev-section__desc wow fadeInUp mb-5">{% if lang == "en" %}From threat modeling on the story to runtime monitoring — security embedded at every gate.{% else %}Do threat modeling na story ao monitoramento runtime — segurança embutida em cada porta.{% endif %}</p>
      <div class="ev-delivery-grid">
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-drafting-compass"></i></div><h4>1. Plan</h4><p>Threat Modeling (STRIDE), abuse stories, data classification, privacy by design.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-code"></i></div><h4>2. Code</h4><p>SAST in IDE, secret scanning, secure coding training, golden paths per language.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-cube"></i></div><h4>3. Build</h4><p>SCA, SBOM, signed container images, hardened base images, IaC scanning.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-vial"></i></div><h4>4. Test</h4><p>DAST in staging, authenticated API fuzzing, contract tests on auth, load with chaos.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-upload"></i></div><h4>5. Release</h4><p>Policy-as-code (OPA), SLSA v1.0, image signing (cosign), change-advisory automation.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-rocket"></i></div><h4>6. Deploy</h4><p>{% if lang == "en" %}Kubernetes admission controllers, GitOps, canary with security gates.{% else %}Admission controllers do Kubernetes, GitOps, canary com security gates.{% endif %}</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-eye"></i></div><h4>7. Operate</h4><p>CSPM, CWPP, RASP, runtime detections on EDR/XDR and SIEM correlations.</p></div>
        <div class="ev-delivery-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-delivery-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i></div><h4>8. Monitor</h4><p>MTTR by severity, escape rate, coverage %, ratio SAST/DAST/SCA fix vs. backlog.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MID-PAGE CTA -->
  <section style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(0,224,163,.12) 0%,rgba(0,224,163,.03) 100%);border-top:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.2);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.2);padding:40px 0;">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="row align-items-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
          <h3 style="font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:8px;color:#fff;">
            {% if lang == "en" %}Want to implement this pipeline in your organization?{% else %}Quer implementar esse pipeline na sua organização?{% endif %}
          </h3>
          <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);margin:0;font-size:.95rem;">
            {% if lang == "en" %}Free 30-minute conversation with a DevSecOps architect to map your current state.{% else %}30 min gratuitos com um arquiteto DevSecOps para mapear seu estado atual.{% endif %}
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-4 text-lg-right">
          <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/contact" class="contact-btn">{% if lang == "en" %}Talk to a specialist{% else %}Falar com especialista{% endif %}</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7 KPIs -->
  <section class="ev-section ev-section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Measurement{% else %}Medição{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}7 KPIs executives understand{% else %}7 KPIs que o board entende{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="row mt-5">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mx-auto">
          {% set kpis = [
            { name: "MTTR por severidade", name_en: "MTTR by severity", desc_pt: "Tempo para corrigir Critical / High / Medium / Low. Meta: Crítico < 7 dias.", desc_en: "Time to fix Critical / High / Medium / Low. Target: Critical < 7 days." },
            { name: "Escape rate", name_en: "Escape rate", desc_pt: "% de vulnerabilidades encontradas em produção que deveriam ter sido pegas antes. Meta: < 10%.", desc_en: "% of vulnerabilities found in production that should have been caught earlier. Target: < 10%." },
            { name: "Pipeline coverage", name_en: "Pipeline coverage", desc_pt: "% de repositórios com SAST + SCA + secret scanning. Meta: > 90%.", desc_en: "% of repositories with SAST + SCA + secret scanning. Target: > 90%." },
            { name: "Vulnerability age", name_en: "Vulnerability age", desc_pt: "Idade média dos achados críticos abertos. Meta: < 30 dias.", desc_en: "Average age of open critical findings. Target: < 30 days." },
            { name: "Deploy frequency", name_en: "Deploy frequency", desc_pt: "Métrica DORA: frequência de deploy seguro. DevSecOps não pode travar entregas.", desc_en: "DORA metric: how often we deploy safely. DevSecOps should not slow delivery." },
            { name: "Change failure rate", name_en: "Change failure rate", desc_pt: "Deploys que causam incidentes. DORA + segurança.", desc_en: "Deploys that cause incidents. DORA + security." },
            { name: "Dependency freshness", name_en: "Dependency freshness", desc_pt: "% de dependências dentro de 6 meses da mais recente. Meta: > 80%.", desc_en: "% of dependencies within 6 months of latest. Target: > 80%." }
          ] %}
          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;">
            {% for kpi in kpis %}
            <div class="wow fadeInUp" style="display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:16px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.03);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);border-radius:12px;padding:18px 22px;transition:border-color .2s,background .2s;" onmouseover="this.style.borderColor='rgba(0,224,163,.25)';this.style.background='rgba(0,224,163,.05)'" onmouseout="this.style.borderColor='rgba(255,255,255,.07)';this.style.background='rgba(255,255,255,.03)'">
              <div style="min-width:32px;height:32px;background:rgba(0,224,163,.15);border:1px solid rgba(0,224,163,.3);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;flex-shrink:0;">
                <span style="color:#00e0a3;font-weight:800;font-size:.82rem;">{{ loop.index }}</span>
              </div>
              <div style="padding-top:4px;">
                <strong style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.95rem;">{{ kpi.name_en if lang == "en" else kpi.name }}</strong>
                <span style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);font-size:.9rem;"> — {{ kpi.desc_en if lang == "en" else kpi.desc_pt }}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endfor %}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4 ERROS -->
  <section class="ev-section bg-overly-img">
    <div class="container overlay-content">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Watch out{% else %}Atenção{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}4 mistakes that kill 80% of DevSecOps programs{% else %}4 erros que matam 80% dos programas DevSecOps{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="ev-pain-grid mt-4">
        <div class="ev-pain-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-pain-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-ban"></i></div><p><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Security-as-a-gatekeeper{% else %}Segurança como gatekeeper{% endif %}</strong> — {% if lang == "en" %}blocking deploys without context kills credibility and bypass grows.{% else %}bloquear deploy sem contexto mata credibilidade e vira bypass.{% endif %}</p></div>
        <div class="ev-pain-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-pain-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-tools"></i></div><p><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Tools without process{% else %}Ferramentas sem processo{% endif %}</strong> — {% if lang == "en" %}buying 5 platforms without model, RACI or SLA produces shelfware.{% else %}comprar 5 plataformas sem modelo, RACI e SLA gera shelfware.{% endif %}</p></div>
        <div class="ev-pain-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-pain-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-user-slash"></i></div><p><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}Zero developer ownership{% else %}Zero ownership do dev{% endif %}</strong> — {% if lang == "en" %}if a developer does not see, fix and close findings, there is no DevSecOps.{% else %}se o dev não vê, não corrige e não fecha achados, não existe DevSecOps.{% endif %}</p></div>
        <div class="ev-pain-card wow fadeInUp"><div class="ev-pain-card__icon"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i></div><p><strong>{% if lang == "en" %}No executive KPIs{% else %}Sem KPIs executivos{% endif %}</strong> — {% if lang == "en" %}without MTTR, escape rate and coverage, the program has no ROI narrative.{% else %}sem MTTR, escape rate e coverage, o programa não tem narrativa de ROI.{% endif %}</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- RELACIONADOS -->
  <section class="ev-section ev-section--alt">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="ev-section__tag wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Go deeper{% else %}Aprofunde{% endif %}</div>
      <h2 class="ev-section__title wow fadeInUp">{% if lang == "en" %}Related content{% else %}Conteúdos relacionados{% endif %}</h2>
      <div class="ev-related-grid mt-4">
        <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/guias/sast-vs-dast-vs-sca/" class="ev-related-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(0,224,163,.1);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:12px;"><i class="fas fa-search-plus" style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.9rem;"></i></div>
          <h5>SAST vs DAST vs SCA</h5>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Differences, blind spots and how to combine them in CI/CD.{% else %}Diferenças, pontos cegos e como combinar no CI/CD.{% endif %}</p>
        </a>
        <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/solucoes/secure-code/" class="ev-related-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(0,224,163,.1);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:12px;"><i class="fas fa-shield-alt" style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.9rem;"></i></div>
          <h5>Secure Code</h5>
          <p>{% if lang == "en" %}Evernow Secure Code pillar: AppSec + DevSecOps end-to-end.{% else %}Pilar Secure Code da Evernow: AppSec + DevSecOps ponta a ponta.{% endif %}</p>
        </a>
        <a href="{{ urlPrefix }}/produtos/devsecops/" class="ev-related-card wow fadeInUp">
          <div style="width:36px;height:36px;background:rgba(0,224,163,.1);border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:12px;"><i class="fas fa-cogs" style="color:#00e0a3;font-size:.9rem;"></i></div>
